--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
OBLIGATIONS CARRIED FORWARD / CAVEATS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. CMMI definitions (third-party copyright). The source guideline draws its
   formal definitions of "verification" and "validation" from CMMI for
   Development, Version 1.2 (Carnegie Mellon Software Engineering Institute,
   2006), a separately copyrighted process model. This pack PARAPHRASES those
   concepts throughout and reproduces NO verbatim CMMI text. Any CMMI wording
   should be cited to the SEI, not copied from this pack.

2. Policy-snapshot caveat. The source's V&V phase tables (Tables 1–6) reflect
   FAA AMS policy as of April 2017 and are expressly superseded by current FAA
   phase guidelines and templates. Reproduced table content (criteria,
   responsible offices, form/order numbers, organizational names) is illustrative
   of the model, not live regulatory authority.

3. No third-party material is reproduced. This pack contains only synthesized,
   paraphrased reference notes — no source figures, tables, or extended verbatim
   passages.

